About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cQA3TWG8mHLCRO_vFhMoYiV

snippet.title: Living like a Mermaid üßú‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è for a day!
snippet.description:
üßú‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è Living Like a Mermaid for a Day! üåä Dive into an enchanting underwater adventure as we take on the ultimate mermaid challenge. Join us on this magical journey as we transform into mermaids and explore the wonders of the ocean! üê†

In this captivating vlog, we'll show you how we prepared for our day as mermaids, including getting our mermaid tails, creating mesmerizing mermaid makeup looks, and styling our hair with shimmering shells and pearls. üßú‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è‚ú®

Once we're fully transformed, we'll take you along as we dive into the crystal-clear waters, swimming gracefully like real mermaids. Get ready to witness stunning underwater footage as we encounter colorful marine life, mystical coral reefs, and maybe even discover hidden treasures! üêöüåà

But being a mermaid isn't just about swimming. We'll also indulge in delightful mermaid-themed snacks and drinks, perfecting our mermaid poses and dances, and enjoying the magical serenity of the ocean's embrace. It's a day filled with joy, wonder, and a touch of mermaid magic! üåäüéâ

So, if you've ever wondered what it's like to live as a mermaid, or simply want to embark on a whimsical adventure with us, don't miss this extraordinary experience. Dive into the deep blue with us and let your imagination swim free in this unforgettable mermaid journey! üßú‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏èüíô

Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe to our channel to stay tuned for more incredible adventures. Hit that notification bell so you never miss a moment of our magical escapades! üîî‚ú®

Tere Bin Episode 56 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 22nd June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

#drdanishsalim #danishsalim #drdbetterlife #dybarism #titanic #submarine*****Dr.
 Danish Salim*****

Dr Danish Salim; currently working as Specialist Emergency Department, Sheikh Khalifa Medical City, Abu Dubai, UAE Health Authority & Managing Director at Dr D Better Life Pvt Ltd. He was the academic director and head of the emergency department at PRS Hospital, Kerala. He has over 10 years of experience in emergency and critical care. He was awarded the SEHA Hero award and is one of the first doctors to receive a Golden Visa from the UAE Government for his contributions to Health Care.

He was active in the field of emergency medicine and have
contributed in bringing in multiple innovations for which Dr
Danish was awarded nationally as "Best innovator in emergency medicine and young achiever" as well as the ‚ÄúBest emergency physician of state award".

Among multiple innovations like app for accident alerts, jump kits for common emergency management, Dr Danish brought into being the state's first bike ambulance with KED and a single state wide-app to control and coordinate private and public ambulances under one platform with the help of Indian Medical Association and Kerala Police. This network was appreciated and is successfully running with the support of the government of Kerala currently.

Besides the technology field, Dr Danish was enthusiastic in conducting more than 2000 structured emergency training classes for common men, residents, doctors and healthcare professionals over the span of 5 years.

Positions Held

1. Kerala state Secretary: Society for Emergency Medicine India

2. National Innovation Head Society for Emergency Medicine India

3. Vice President Indian Medical Association Kovalam

#drdanishsalim #danishsalim #drdbetterlife #dybarism #titanic #submarine*****Dr.
 Danish Salim*****

Dr Danish Salim; currently working as Specialist Emergency Department, Sheikh Khalifa Medical City, Abu Dubai, UAE Health Authority & Managing Director at Dr D Better Life Pvt Ltd. He was the academic director and head of the emergency department at PRS Hospital, Kerala. He has over 10 years of experience in emergency and critical care. He was awarded the SEHA Hero award and is one of the first doctors to receive a Golden Visa from the UAE Government for his contributions to Health Care.

He was active in the field of emergency medicine and have
contributed in bringing in multiple innovations for which Dr
Danish was awarded nationally as "Best innovator in emergency medicine and young achiever" as well as the ‚ÄúBest emergency physician of state award".

Among multiple innovations like app for accident alerts, jump kits for common emergency management, Dr Danish brought into being the state's first bike ambulance with KED and a single state wide-app to control and coordinate private and public ambulances under one platform with the help of Indian Medical Association and Kerala Police. This network was appreciated and is successfully running with the support of the government of Kerala currently.

Besides the technology field, Dr Danish was enthusiastic in conducting more than 2000 structured emergency training classes for common men, residents, doctors and healthcare professionals over the span of 5 years.

Positions Held

1. Kerala state Secretary: Society for Emergency Medicine India

2. National Innovation Head Society for Emergency Medicine India

3. Vice President Indian Medical Association Kovalam

snippet.title: Kamala Harris Bursts into Laughter after PM Modi's this Comment at U.S. Congress | Watch
snippet.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi lauded Indian-origin US Vice President Kamala Harris while addressing the joint sitting of the US Congress and referred to "significant presence of millions of individuals in the United States who have ancestral ties to India." Modi, in a lighter vein, said "samosa caucus is now the flavour of the House" and hoped that more Indian foods are included in the future.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3805 | 23 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3805: Important Meeting Ki Tyaari
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha is worried about his client meeting tomorrow because his pal Taarak will be unavailable. Taarak pays Jetha a visit after dinner and proposes he takes Bagha and Nattu Kaka because they are fluent in English and know a lot about the company. Jetha phones Bagha and requests an instant meeting, but Bagha is preoccupied with Bawri. As a result, Jetha and Taarak decide to pay a visit to Bagha and Nattu Kaka. Taarak informs Bagha and Nattu Kaka about their managing meeting. Nattu Kaka believes it would be strange if Jetha, as the owner, remained mute while his employers dealt with the clients. So, what happens next? Will Taarak devise a new strategy?

snippet.title: Challengers - Official Trailer - Warner Bros. UK & Ireland
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for #ChallengersMovie starring Zendaya, Josh O‚ÄôConnor, and Mike Faist. Directed by Luca Guadagnino, only in cinemas September 15.

From visionary filmmaker Luca Guadagnino, Challengers stars Zendaya as Tashi Duncan, a former tennis prodigy turned coach and a force of nature who makes no apologies for her game on and off the court. Married to a champion on a losing streak (Mike Faist ‚Äì West Side Story), Tashi‚Äôs strategy for her husband‚Äôs redemption takes a surprising turn when he must face off against the washed-up Patrick (Josh O‚ÄôConnor ‚Äì The Crown) ‚Äì his former best friend and Tashi‚Äôs former boyfriend. As their pasts and presents collide, and tensions run high, Tashi must ask herself, what will it cost to win.

           Yeh kahani hai ek sidhi sadhi, padhi likhi, pyaari si, Pratigya aur ameer, bigdel, badtameez Krishna ki. snippet.description: Rashtriya Janta Dal locates itself in the collective aspirations of people and communities striving to carve out a society based on the premises of social justice and secularism. Since its inception Rashtriya Janta Dal is relentlessly working as the voice of the socially and economically downtrodden sections of the society. The RJD believes in working on and propagating socialist politics and towrds this end the party has been developing solidarity network of landless labourers, peasants and farmers other weaker groups as well as progressive people from other sections of society. Drawing inspiration from Gandhian values as well as following in the great tradition of the socialist leaders, RJD strongly stands against communalism in any form. The party believes that the right of peaceful and democratic dissent including Satyagraha/ non-violent resistance is a fundamental right of the people.

snippet.title: NEW! Baalveer S3 | Ep 37 | 23 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 37: Kaashvi Ka Pehla Jurm
-------------------------------------------------
Baalveer looks for his mother in Udaka Lok but is unable to locate her. Shaashmaag learns from surveillance that Baalveer has violated the boundaries of Udaka Lok. He summons Baalveer and tries to have him arrested along with one of his henchmen. Baalveer poses as a regular lad from Dharti Lok who stumbled onto this mysterious location. Shaashmaag arrests Baalveer and brings him to Maha Mahim Uttan because she doesn't believe him. Aageel is busy hatching her cunning scheme to control Kaashvi through Maha Jadoo. Will Kaashvi commit human sins while under Aageel's sway?

Show Name ‚Äì Baalveer S3
Star Cast ‚Äì Dev Joshi, Aditi Sanwal, Ada Khan, Behzaad Khan, Aditya Ranvijay
Episodes No - 37, 23 June 2023
Produced By - Vipul D Shah

About the show: 
---------------------------
The new season of Baalveer follows the journey of the 24-year-old superhero who draws strength from his mother. In this season, Baalveer is stripped of his powers, magic, and memories and lives as a regular boy Veer. The season revolves around his journey from Veer to Baalveer, regaining his identity and the world he belongs to with the help of partner Kaashvi.

snippet.description:

Episode 3804: Taarak Ka Special Day
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak is very excited to celebrate his anniversary with Anjali, as his boss has granted him a day off. Jetha has received a dealership letter from one of his most anticipated clients. The client has scheduled a meeting for tomorrow, which is a very short span of time. Jetha needs Taarak's aid to attend the meeting, as the meeting will be conducted in English and Jetha struggles to communicate in the language. Taarak plans a surprise for Anjali to break the news, but Sodhi comes in and jeopardizes everything. What will Taarak do now? Will he spend his day with his beloved wife or support his best friend Jetha? Who will Taarak choose to be with?

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

*About* 
------------

           Yeh kahani hai ek sidhi sadhi, padhi likhi, pyaari si, Pratigya aur ameer, bigdel, badtameez Krishna ki. Pratigya ki parvarish hui ek sadharan par acche parivaar mein jaha padhai aur sanskaron ko diya gaya bohot mahatva. Wahi doosri taraf apne parivaar mein Krishna ne dekhi zulm aur paise ki taakat. Isi taakat ke dum par zabardasti ki Krishna ne Pratigya se shaadi. 
           Pratigya ke sasural aur maayke mein hai zameen aur aasmaan ka faasla. Krishna ki haveli mein prem aur aadar ka hai akaal. Aise mein kya hoga Pratigya ka haal? Waqt ke sath Pratigya- Krishna ne kiya hazaaron mushkilon ka saamna aur door hua dono ke beech ka faasla. Ek anchaha rishta ban gaya sacche pyaar ki misaal.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: ‡§â‡§∏ ‡§≤‡§°‡§º‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§ï‡•ã ‡§¨‡•ã‡§≤ ‡§ö‡•Å‡§ï‡•á ‡§•‡•á IAS ‡§¨‡§®‡§ï‡§∞ ‡§¶‡§ø‡§ñ‡§æ‡§è‡§Ç‡§ó‡•á | Aaditya Pandey | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Aaditya Pandey has brought AIR-48 to the UPSC examination 2023 and will become IAS. Once people used to tell their father that their son will not be able to do anything. Then somehow he did engineering and then did MBA. Then he had a breakup, after which he decided that he would crack UPSC. After working hard for 3 years and failing twice in UPSC, he cracked UPSC and got AIR-48.
